Type: Effect
Name: Shock
Initial DC: +2
Addt'l DC: +2
DC Bonus: +1 to Threat Die Size
Description: A [Effect]Shock Spell creates a intense, breif surge of electrical energy. The effect causes a Threat[Shock], (Threat DC=10+1d6+Casting Stat). The effect of this spell can be intensified, increasing the Threat Dice Size. To increase the Threat Dice Size, add +2 to the Mana DC of the Spell Word, for every Threat Die step.
